" and report data at national level about domestic resources allocated for "
"the implementation of DLDD activities and programs, including through "
"national budgetary processes."
msgstr ""
"Identificación de expertos para verificar la fiabilidad de los registros de "
"información sobre flujos de recursos relacionados con la DDTS y actividades "
