"preferiblemente proporcionando un enlace a la documentación subyacente."

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../SO5.md:184
msgid ""
"Under Tier 2, the template provides a summary table with quantitative "
"aggregated data. The table shows total amounts of international private "
"resources provided, international private resources received, and domestic "
"private resources mobilized, for each year of the reporting period. All "
"amounts relate to actual amounts of funds that have been paid or received "
